JetV raced along the hilly terrain, he knew the land well now as he 
shot out of a group of trees and off a rise in the hill.  While in the air 
he transformed to his bot mode letting loose two shots from his 
rifle.  The shots hit two trees down by the beach raised up on the 
cliff a bit.  The trees fell toward the ground making a ramp down 
into the water.  Before he hit the groudn he transformed again into 
a JetSki.  Landing in between the two logs he slid into the water 
and resumed course.  Dunking under the water he shot back up 
100 meters later transforming to his ATV with a saw buzzing as he 
went straight into a groupd of trees.  Moments later he appeared on 
the ground, trees falling behind him.  "Almostt here" he said.
